		<div class="entry-content"><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/16/today-in-small-business-dont-turn-left/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Don&#8217;t Turn Left" data-description="The good side of a bad online review. Stop trying to go viral. And does the S.B.A. make it too easy for banks to lend money to small businesses?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ This is <a href="//advisorperspectives.com/dshort/guest/Lance-Roberts-140415-Economy-in-Pictures.php">the economy</a> in charts.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Rising food and housing costs are <a href="//finance.yahoo.com/news/food-rental-housing-bump-u-123230865.html">pushing up</a> inflation, which could cause your <a href="//time.com/61870/your-grilling-season-budget-just-went-up-in-smoke/">grilling season budget</a> to up in smoke.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Coca-Cola sales <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/04/15/us-cocacola-results-idUSBREA3E0R220140415?f">beat estimates</a> thanks to China.</p>
